{
  "text": "The median age of the children infected with RV G1P [CITATION_1] and G2P [CITATION_2] was identical (21 months, p = 0.7). The unusual G8P [CITATION_3] strains detected between April and May 2007, and G8P [CITATION_4] in October, were collected mainly from children younger than 24 months of age. The other genotypes appeared sporadically (Fig. 2, right axis) .",
